The paper deals with privacy protection and statistical inference, which are common topics in the computer security (cs.CR) and machine learning (cs.LG) communities. The paper also discusses optimization and quantization techniques, which are relevant to information theory (cs.IT) and data structures (cs.DS). Finally, the paper evaluates its method on datasets, which suggests a connection to databases (cs.DB).
